{"type":"message","id":"ff09f8a9","parentId":"94d8b848","timestamp":"2026-04-03T13:04:14.847Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好的！既然你已经启动了Claude Code，那么它现在应该已经登录并可以正常工作了。\n\n现在我可以帮你与Claude Code交互，或者启动一个Claude Code会话来处理任务。你想让我：\n\n1. **启动一个新的Claude Code会话**来处理特定任务？\n2. **与现有的Claude Code会话交互**？\n3. **展示Claude Code的基本用法**？\n\n请告诉我你想让Claude Code做什么，我会使用正确的参数启动它。根据技能说明，对于Claude Code，我应该使用：\n\n```bash\nclaude --permission-mode bypassPermissions --print '你的任务描述'\n```\n\n或者如果需要后台运行：\n```bash\nbash workdir:/path/to/project background:true command:\"claude --permission-mode bypassPermissions --print '你的任务描述'\"\n```\n\n你想在哪个目录运行Claude Code？比如之前提到的 `/mnt/d/cod` 目录，还是其他位置？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":105,"output":191,"cacheRead":25408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25704,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775221449219,"responseId":"4b397d78-3e02-4060-81f6-865431d7002b"}}
