{"type":"message","id":"980ba3ab","parentId":"9fa84e6f","timestamp":"2026-04-03T13:04:33.591Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好的，我来尝试与Claude Code进行交互。我会启动一个Claude Code会话，并尝试发送一个简单的任务，看看是否能得到响应。\n\n首先，让我在 `/mnt/d/cod` 目录下启动一个Claude Code会话，让它做一个简单的任务："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_S1bsv3uWdlX5Iw8DtWOZ838q","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /mnt/d/cod && claude --permission-mode bypassPermissions --print \"请用Python写一个'Hello World'程序，并解释代码。\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":101,"output":131,"cacheRead":25664,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25896,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775221469130,"responseId":"c50c83a6-25c9-429a-bc3c-c8f92454ffbf"}}
