{"type":"message","id":"f6dd6624","parentId":"20babe9b","timestamp":"2026-04-03T13:04:39.746Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"看起来即使你启动了Claude Code，我这边仍然显示需要登录。这可能是因为：\n\n1. **认证是会话特定的**：你的Claude Code登录可能只在你的终端会话中有效\n2. **环境变量不同**：我的环境可能没有继承你的认证信息\n3. **认证方式不同**：Claude Code可能使用基于会话的认证\n\n让我尝试几种不同的方法来交互：\n\n## 方法1：检查是否有环境变量或配置文件"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_2Kav7uosd0EcpHW0s3FBWYly","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"env | grep -E \"(ANTHROPIC|CLAUDE)\" | head -10"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":265,"output":153,"cacheRead":25664,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26082,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775221474838,"responseId":"2365525e-3d95-4dc1-b505-3a8000bd2d76"}}
