{"type":"message","id":"5c1aa07a","parentId":"ef894bbe","timestamp":"2026-04-03T13:14:35.978Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"你说得对！我们说的确实不是同一个东西。\n\n你在Windows里安装了一个**Claude Code**，并且通过Ollama配置了本地模型。而我（OpenClaw助理）运行在WSL2环境中，使用的是另一个配置。\n\n让我理清一下：\n\n1. **你的环境**：Windows系统，安装了Claude Code，配置了Ollama本地模型\n2. **我的环境**：WSL2（Linux），有Claude Code CLI，但配置的是OpenRouter API\n\n**关键问题**：我的WSL环境可能无法直接访问你在Windows中配置的Claude Code认证和Ollama模型。\n\n## 解决方案\n\n### 方案1：检查WSL是否能访问Windows的Ollama\n让我检查WSL中是否能访问Ollama服务："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_foc3umYOMSoGFtI6y25MpM63","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s http://localhost:11434/api/tags 2>/dev/null | head -5"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":142,"output":225,"cacheRead":29120,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29487,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775222069072,"responseId":"25bc3759-e5de-475b-906d-833592f3a067"}}
