{"type":"message","id":"5639847b","parentId":"24d9160b","timestamp":"2026-04-03T13:14:47.587Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_knQ5dT78QPd1wyu4IZWOTtaP","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"--bare                                            Minimal mode: skip hooks, LSP, plugin sync, attribution, auto-memory, background prefetches, keychain reads, and CLAUDE.md auto-discovery. Sets CLAUDE_CODE_SIMPLE=1. Anthropic auth is strictly ANTHROPIC_API_KEY or apiKeyHelper via --settings (OAuth and keychain are never read). 3P providers (Bedrock/Vertex/Foundry) use their own credentials. Skills still resolve via /skill-name. Explicitly provide context via: --system-prompt[-file], --append-system-prompt[-file], --add-dir (CLAUDE.md dirs), --mcp-config, --settings, --agents, --plugin-dir."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":700,"aggregated":"--bare                                            Minimal mode: skip hooks, LSP, plugin sync, attribution, auto-memory, background prefetches, keychain reads, and CLAUDE.md auto-discovery. Sets CLAUDE_CODE_SIMPLE=1. Anthropic auth is strictly ANTHROPIC_API_KEY or apiKeyHelper via --settings (OAuth and keychain are never read). 3P providers (Bedrock/Vertex/Foundry) use their own credentials. Skills still resolve via /skill-name. Explicitly provide context via: --system-prompt[-file], --append-system-prompt[-file], --add-dir (CLAUDE.md dirs), --mcp-config, --settings, --agents, --plugin-dir.","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775222087582}}
{"type":"message","id":"2ef5e9e6","parentId":"5639847b","timestamp":"2026-04-03T13:14:52.138Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"根据帮助信息，Claude Code支持\"3P providers (Bedrock/Vertex/Foundry)\"，但可能也支持Ollama。让我尝试配置Claude Code使用Ollama。\n\n首先，让我尝试直接使用Ollama API："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_c6GGh1W0UuNNWQGZxAeNNYAp","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -X POST http://host.docker.internal:11434/api/generate -d '{\"model\": \"qwen2.5:14b\", \"prompt\": \"你好\", \"stream\": false}' | head -5"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":1390,"output":142,"cacheRead":29568,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31100,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775222087588,"responseId":"440a9cff-2ab1-47bf-8756-04f3280a3ac8"}}
