{"type":"message","id":"d18603fb","parentId":"f9be1d9c","timestamp":"2026-04-03T13:15:05.067Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"很好！Ollama工作正常。现在让我尝试配置Claude Code使用Ollama。我需要创建一个使用Ollama的配置。\n\n让我尝试使用 `--settings` 参数配置Ollama："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_PUCeLSOfTivz77KHNNHXbAZf","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"timeout 10 claude --bare --settings '{\"provider\": \"ollama\", \"model\": \"qwen2.5:14b\", \"apiBaseUrl\": \"http://host.docker.internal:11434\"}' --print \"你好\" 2>&1"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":283,"output":140,"cacheRead":31040,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31463,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775222100613,"responseId":"f2225008-2087-48e2-8b18-9be3ca198f55"}}
