{"type":"message","id":"7a208b65","parentId":"10e4b26b","timestamp":"2026-04-03T13:15:10.320Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"仍然需要登录。让我尝试不同的方法。也许Claude Code需要特定的Ollama配置格式。\n\n## 方案3：直接使用Ollama CLI\n既然Ollama工作正常，我可以直接使用Ollama CLI，而不是通过Claude Code："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_obLnR6YtcpGKzejJ5zs73JbN","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"which ollama 2>/dev/null || echo \"Ollama CLI未在WSL中安装\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":72,"output":116,"cacheRead":31424,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31612,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775222106293,"responseId":"f251fc13-0480-4d29-95d4-84eaf1572032"}}
