{"type":"message","id":"a6ad52ec","parentId":"c097fb5d","timestamp":"2026-04-03T13:15:17.812Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ollama CLI没有在WSL中安装，但我可以通过curl直接调用Ollama API。\n\n## 当前最佳方案\n\n既然Claude Code需要登录而无法直接使用，但Ollama API工作正常，我建议：\n\n### 方案A：你直接在Windows终端中使用Claude Code\n既然你已经在Windows中安装并配置了Claude Code，最直接的方式是你在Windows终端中直接使用它。\n\n### 方案B：我通过Ollama API直接与模型交互\n我可以编写脚本通过Ollama API直接与你的本地模型交互，处理编码任务。\n\n### 方案C：配置Claude Code的认证\n如果你能在Windows中完成Claude Code的登录，然后WSL可能能共享认证信息。\n\n## 建议\n\n**最简单的方式**：你直接在Windows终端中使用Claude Code，因为它已经配置好了。\n\n**如果你希望我处理任务**：我可以：\n1. 通过Ollama API直接调用模型\n2. 或者使用我自己的模型（deepseek/deepseek-chat）\n3. 或者你告诉我任务，我生成代码/解决方案\n\n你想采用哪种方式？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":87,"output":236,"cacheRead":31552,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31875,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775222110335,"responseId":"85a0bc03-c358-4cc4-8447-75382f7b740e"}}
{"type":"message","id":"96d6edb2","parentId":"a6ad52ec","timestamp":"2026-04-03T13:22:27.614Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Fri 2026-04-03 21:22 GMT+8] 解决方案：让 OpenClaw 也能看到这些环境变量\n有两种可靠的方法，推荐使用第一种。\n\n方法一：将环境变量写入 OpenClaw 的服务配置文件（推荐）\n这样 OpenClaw 的网关服务每次启动都会自动加载。\n\n编辑 OpenClaw 网关的环境文件：\n\nbash\nmkdir -p ~/.config/openclaw\nnano ~/.config/openclaw/env\n在文件中添加以下内容（根据你的实际情况）：\n\nbash\nANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN=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\nANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://openrouter.ai/api/v1 # 如果是 OpenRouter，填这个；如果是其他代理，改成你的地址\n# 如果希望 Claude Code 不弹出任何浏览器交互，可以再加上：\n# CLAUDE_CODE_NO_UPDATE_CHECK=1\n# CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_TELEMETRY=1\n重启 OpenClaw 网关：\n\nbash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n验证：可以临时运行 openclaw gateway logs 查看是否有错误。 怎么说"}],"timestamp":1775222547612}}
{"type":"message","id":"318be6aa","parentId":"96d6edb2","timestamp":"2026-04-03T13:22:31.350Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"你说得对！这是一个很好的解决方案。通过配置OpenClaw网关的环境变量，可以让Claude Code在OpenClaw的环境中也能访问到认证信息。\n\n让我按照你的建议来操作：\n\n## 步骤1：创建OpenClaw环境配置文件"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_wdjN44GS3Zv3M3oG54afTVNy","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p ~/.config/openclaw && echo \"创建目录成功\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":312,"output":107,"cacheRead":31872,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32291,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775222547614,"responseId":"36b367a0-e162-49ce-a80e-dae5f40e23bb"}}
