{"type":"message","id":"0b2147d6","parentId":"90fb9eba","timestamp":"2026-04-03T13:22:41.042Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 步骤2：编辑环境文件\n根据你提供的配置，我需要添加环境变量。不过，我需要确认几个事情：\n\n1. **ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN**：你提供的这个令牌是OpenRouter的API密钥吗？\n2. **ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL**：你希望使用OpenRouter还是直接使用Ollama？\n\n根据之前的发现，你有两种选择：\n- **选项1**：使用OpenRouter（配置中的`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`）\n- **选项2**：使用Ollama本地模型（`http://host.docker.internal:11434`）\n\n让我先尝试**选项2：配置Ollama**，因为这是你本地的模型。但Claude Code可能不支持直接配置Ollama作为provider。\n\n让我先尝试**选项1：使用OpenRouter配置**，使用现有的API密钥："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Ll7eOf5cq71MW4aIoCZEDxuD","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"~/.config/openclaw/env","content":"ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN=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\nANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://openrouter.ai/api/v1\nCLAUDE_CODE_NO_UPDATE_CHECK=1\nCLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_TELEMETRY=1"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":439,"output":366,"cacheRead":31872,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32677,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775222551366,"responseId":"8351073d-7e30-4d86-9f5b-5aa5176f9e70"}}
