{"type":"message","id":"46015748","parentId":"305bb88f","timestamp":"2026-04-03T13:25:32.863Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"配置文件中已经有API密钥了。但Claude Code仍然要求登录。这可能是因为：\n\n1. **API密钥无效或已过期**\n2. **Claude Code需要完成一次OAuth流程**（即使有API密钥）\n3. **需要设置额外的环境变量**\n\n让我尝试直接设置环境变量然后运行Claude Code："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_7RvhhUc4s8kuI2OcGQ5SwqdC","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN=\"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\" ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=\"https://openrouter.ai/api/v1\" claude --permission-mode bypassPermissions --print \"测试\" 2>&1 | head -10"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":279,"output":195,"cacheRead":35520,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35994,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775222726038,"responseId":"ca6744a5-86ce-4509-97fa-59308e9a0e75"}}
