{"type":"message","id":"86fdaea6","parentId":"5ef54a7a","timestamp":"2026-04-03T13:25:46.130Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"进步了！现在不是\"Not logged in\"错误，而是模型访问问题。Claude Code默认尝试使用`claude-sonnet-4-6`模型，但这个模型可能：\n1. 在OpenRouter上不可用\n2. 需要不同的API密钥\n3. 需要付费\n\n让我指定使用`deepseek/deepseek-chat`模型："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_kLq2DCLdvYjSYLGdLUx9Zh0m","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN=\"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\" ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=\"https://openrouter.ai/api/v1\" claude --model \"deepseek/deepseek-chat\" --permission-mode bypassPermissions --print \"请写一个Python Hello World程序\" 2>&1"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":83,"output":218,"cacheRead":35968,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36269,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775222738860,"responseId":"1f9f7d91-a092-4322-9359-528ab413dd87"}}
