fig/openclaw/env\n在文件中添加以下内容（根据你的实际情况）：\n\nbash\nANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN=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\nANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://openrouter.ai/api/v1 # 如果是 OpenRouter，填这个；如果是其他代理，改成你的地址\n# 如果希望 Claude Code 不弹出任何浏览器交互，可以再加上：\n# CLAUDE_CODE_NO_UPDATE_C...\n- Assistant: 你说得对！这是一个很好的解决方案。通过配置OpenClaw网关的环境变量，可以让Claude Code在OpenClaw的环境中也能访问到认证信息。\n\n让我按照你的建议来操作：\n\n## 步骤1：创建OpenClaw环境配置文件\n[non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (exec): 创建目录成功\n- Assistant: ## 步骤2：编辑环境文件\n根据你提供的配置，我需要添加环境变量。不过，我需要确认几个事情：\n\n1. **ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN**：你提供的这个令牌是OpenRouter的API密钥吗？\n2. **ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL**：你希望使用OpenRouter还是直接使用Ollama？\n\n根据之前的发现，你有两种选择：\n- **选项1**：使用OpenRouter（配置中的`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`）\n- **选项2**：使用Ollama本地模型（`http://host.docker.internal:11434`）\n\n让我先尝试**选项2：配置Ollama**，因为这是你本地的模型。但Claude Code可能不支持直接配置Ollama作为provider。\n\n让我先尝试**选项1：使用OpenRouter配置**，使用现有的API密钥：\n[non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (write): Successfully wrote 204 bytes to ~/.config/openclaw/env\n- Assistant: ## 步骤3：重启OpenClaw网关\n[non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (exec): /bin/bash: openclaw: command not found\n\nCommand not found\n- Assistant: OpenClaw命令不在PATH中。让我检查OpenClaw的安装位置：\n[non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (exec): (no output)\n- Assistant: [non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (exec): (no output)\n- Assistant: 让我检查npm全局安装的包：\n[non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (exec): (no output)\n- Assistant: [non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (exec): lrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai        43 Mar 30 18:16 clawdhub -> ../lib/node_modules/clawhub/bin/clawdhub.js\nlrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai        43 Mar 30 18:16 clawhub -> ../lib/node_modules/clawhub/bin/clawdhub.js\nlrwxrwxrwx 1 ai ai        41 Mar 30 15:04 openclaw -> ../lib/node_modules/openclaw/openclaw.mjs\n- Assistant: 找到了！OpenClaw在 `~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/bin/openclaw`。让我添加这个目录到PATH，或者直接使用完整路径：\n[non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (exec): (Command exited with code 1)\n- User: Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Fri 2026-04-03 21:24 GMT+8] 干嘛呢\n- Assistant: 抱歉，我有点跑偏了。你提供了一个很好的解决方案，但我执行得有点混乱。让我重新整理一下：\n\n## 问题回顾\n1. Claude Code需要登录才能使用\n2. 你建议通过配置OpenClaw环境变量来解决\n3. 我尝试配置但遇到了命令找不到的问题\n\n## 正确的做法\n\n你提供的方案是正确的：**将环境变量写入OpenClaw的服务配置文件**。这样OpenClaw网关服务启动时就会加载这些环境变量，Claude Code就能访问到认证信息。\n\n让我按正确步骤操作：\n\n### 1. 首先检查OpenClaw网关状态\n[non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (exec): ai         12239 14.1  2.5 22589288 411984 ?     Ssl  21:23   0:10 openclaw-gateway\n- Assistant: OpenClaw网关已经在运行（进程ID 12239）。\n\n### 2. 检查OpenClaw的配置目录结构\n[non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (exec): total 16\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 ai ai 4096 Apr  3 21:22 .\ndrwxr-xr-x 8 ai ai 4096 Mar 30 19:31 ..\n-rw-rw-r-- 1 ai ai  204 Apr  3 21:22 env\n-rw-r--r-- 1 ai ai  898 Mar 22 21:36 openclaw.json\n- Assistant: 好的，我已经创建了`env`文件。让我查看一下内容：\n[non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (read): ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN=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\nANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://openrouter.ai/api/v1\nCLAUDE_CODE_NO_UPDATE_CHECK=1\nCLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_TELEMETRY=1\n- Assistant: ### 3. 现在需要重启OpenClaw网关使环境变量生效\n\n但首先，我需要找到正确的OpenClaw命令路径。让我检查：\n[non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (exec): /home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/cloudflare-ai-gateway/openclaw.plugin.json\n/home/ai/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/vercel-ai-gateway/openclaw.plugin.json\n/home/ai/.config/systemd/user/openclaw-gateway.service\n/home/ai/.config/systemd/user/openclaw-gateway.service.bak\n- Assistant: 看起来OpenClaw网关是作为systemd服务运行的。让我检查服务状态：\n[non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (exec): ● openclaw-gateway.service - OpenClaw Gateway (v2026.3.13)\n     Loaded: loaded (/home/ai/.config/systemd/user/openclaw-gateway.service; enabled; vendor preset: enabled)\n     Active: active (running) since Fri 2026-04-03 21:23:17 CST; 1min 32s ago\n   Main PID: 12239 (openclaw-gatewa)\n      Tasks: 14 (limit: 19100)\n     Memory: 357.5M\n        CPU: 11.704s\n     CGroup: /user.slice/user-1000.slice/user@1000.service/openclaw-gateway.service\n             ├─12239 openclaw-gateway\n             ├─12279 /bin/bash -c systemctl --user status openclaw-gateway 2>&1 | head -20\n             ├─12280 systemctl ...\n- Assistant: 很好！OpenClaw网关正在运行。现在我需要重启它来加载新的环境变量。\n\n### 4. 重启OpenClaw网关服务\n[non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (exec): Command aborted by signal SIGTERM\n\n<read-files>\n~/.config/claude/config.json\n~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/coding-agent/SKILL.md\n\n</read-files>\n\n<modified-files>\n~/.config/openclaw/env\n\n</modified-files>","firstKeptEntryId":"f26c4228","tokensBefore":52208,"details":{"readFiles":["~/.config/claude/config.json","~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/coding-agent/SKILL.md"],"modifiedFiles":["~/.config/openclaw/env"]},"fromHook":true}
