{"type":"message","id":"1e798a0b","parentId":"a550b320","timestamp":"2026-04-03T14:11:26.273Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 总结\n\n**Minimax M2.5配置状态**：\n1. ✅ 已更新Claude Code配置文件使用Minimax API密钥和端点\n2. ❌ **API密钥验证失败** - 返回401错误，提示\"login fail\"\n3. ❌ 可能的原因：\n   - API密钥无效或已过期\n   - 认证格式不正确（Minimax可能需要特定的格式）\n   - 模型名称`minimax-m2.5`可能不正确\n\n**建议**：\n1. **验证API密钥**：请确认Minimax API密钥`J99ouXWKXO8Zg5tLqv92YVsPNFhwuZc-z6z2ioeg7VE`是否有效\n2. **检查模型名称**：确认Minimax M2.5的正确模型标识符\n3. **查看文档**：参考Minimax官方文档确认API调用方式\n\n**当前可用的配置**：\n- ✅ **Ollama本地模型**：已配置并可正常使用（`qwen2.5:14b`等）\n- ✅ **OpenRouter**：之前的配置也可用\n- ❌ **Minimax M2.5**：API密钥验证失败\n\n你想：\n1. 继续调试Minimax配置？\n2. 使用现有的Ollama配置？\n3. 尝试其他模型/API？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":421,"output":293,"cacheRead":30464,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31178,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775225478496,"responseId":"9d3ea3c4-30b4-4a32-bde2-091630c89961"}}
