th=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap h-5 w-5\"><polygon points=\"13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2\"></polygon></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white\">Zero Token Limits</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-400\">Code as much as you want. We charge for concurrency, not tokens. Ideal for heavy AI workflows.</p></div><div class=\"group rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.06] bg-white/[0.02] p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-brand-500/30 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-brand-500/[0.04] opacity-0\" style=\"animation:featureFadeUp 0.6s ease-out 0.44999999999999996s forwards\"><div class=\"mb-4 inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-500/10 text-brand-500 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:bg-brand-500/15\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-server h-5 w-5\"><rect width=\"20\" height=\"8\" x=\"2\" y=\"2\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><rect width=\"20\" height=\"8\" x=\"2\" y=\"14\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><line x1=\"6\" x2=\"6.01\" y1=\"6\" y2=\"6\"></line><line x1=\"6\" x2=\"6.01\" y1=\"18\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white\">High-Performance API</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-400\">Engineered for maximum throughput and minimal latency to support complex agentic coding workflows.</p></div><div class=\"group rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.06] bg-white/[0.02] p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-brand-500/30 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-brand-500/[0.04] opacity-0\" style=\"animation:featureFadeUp 0.6s ease-out 0.55s forwards\"><div class=\"mb-4 inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-500/10 text-brand-500 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:bg-brand-500/15\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-cpu h-5 w-5\"><rect x=\"4\" y=\"4\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" rx=\"2\"></rect><rect x=\"9\" y=\"9\" width=\"6\" height=\"6\"></rect><path d=\"M15 2v2\"></path><path d=\"M15 20v2\"></path><path d=\"M2 15h2\"></path><path d=\"M2 9h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 15h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 9h2\"></path><path d=\"M9 2v2\"></path><path d=\"M9 20v2\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white\">State-of-the-Art Models</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-400\">Access top-tier open source foundation models natively integrated and optimized for codebase reasoning.</p></div><div class=\"group rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.06] bg-white/[0.02] p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-brand-500/30 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-brand-500/[0.04] opacity-0\" style=\"animation:featureFadeUp 0.6s ease-out 0.65s forwards\"><div class=\"mb-4 inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-500/10 text-brand-500 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:bg-brand-500/15\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-activity h-5 w-5\"><path d=\"M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white\">Always On</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-400\">No cold starts. Your dedicated lanes are reserved and ready when you are.</p></div><div class=\"group rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.06] bg-white/[0.02] p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-brand-500/30 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-brand-500/[0.04] opacity-0\" style=\"animation:featureFadeUp 0.6s ease-out 0.75s forwards\"><div class=\"mb-4 inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-500/10 text-brand-500 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:bg-brand-500/15\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users h-5 w-5\"><path d=\"M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white\">Team Collaboration</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-400\">Shared workspaces, usage analytics, and centralized billing for teams of any size.</p></div><div class=\"group rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.06] bg-white/[0.02] p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-brand-500/30 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-brand-500/[0.04] opacity-0\" style=\"animation:featureFadeUp 0.6s ease-out 0.85s forwards\"><div class=\"mb-4 inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-500/10 text-brand-500 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:bg-brand-500/15\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield h-5 w-5\"><path d=\"M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white\">Privacy &amp; Compliance</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-400\">Your code never touches training sets or external logs. SOC-2 compliant infrastructure.</p></div></div></div><style>\n      </style></section><!--astro:end--></astro-island> </