-500/25 transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-brand-400 hover:shadow-brand-500/40 hover:scale-[1.02] active:scale-[0.98]\">Get Started<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4 transition-transform duration-200 group-hover:translate-x-0.5\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"#pricing\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] px-8 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-200 hover:border-white/20 hover:bg-white/[0.06]\">View Pricing</a></div><div class=\"mt-14 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3 opacity-0\" style=\"animation:heroFadeUp 0.8s ease-out 0.7s forwards\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-full border border-white/[0.06] bg-white/[0.03] px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-gray-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap h-3.5 w-3.5 text-brand-500\"><polygon points=\"13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2\"></polygon></svg>No Token Limits</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-full border border-white/[0.06] bg-white/[0.03] px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-gray-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield h-3.5 w-3.5 text-brand-500\"><path d=\"M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10\"></path></svg>SOC-2 Compliant</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-full border border-white/[0.06] bg-white/[0.03] px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-gray-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock h-3.5 w-3.5 text-brand-500\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><polyline points=\"12 6 12 12 16 14\"></polyline></svg>99.9% Uptime</span></div></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 transition-opacity duration-500 flex flex-col items-center gap-2 opacity-100\"><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-500 animate-pulse\">Scroll</span><div class=\"w-[30px] h-[50px] rounded-full border-2 border-white/20 flex justify-center p-2 backdrop-blur-sm bg-white/[0.02]\"><div class=\"w-1.5 h-3 bg-brand-500 rounded-full animate-[scroll_1.5s_infinite]\"></div></div></div><style>\n      </style></section><!--astro:end--></astro-island> <script data-cfasync=\"false\" src=\"/cdn-cgi/scripts/5c5dd728/cloudflare-static/email-decode.min.js\"></script><script>(()=>{var a=(s,i,o)=>{let r=async()=>{await(await s())()},t=typeof i.value==\"object\"?i.value:void 0,c={rootMargin:t==null?void 0:t.rootMargin},n=new IntersectionObserver(e=>{for(let l of e)if(l.isIntersecting){n.disconnect(),r();break}},c);for(let e of o.children)n.observe(e)};(self.Astro||(self.Astro={})).visible=a;window.dispatchEvent(new Event(\"astro:visible\"));})();</script><astro-island uid=\"ZzR5Av\" prefix=\"r10\" component-url=\"/_astro/NewFeatures.D0PA6y4D.js\" component-export=\"default\" renderer-url=\"/_astro/client.BUMBIz6o.js\" props=\"{}\" ssr client=\"visible\" opts=\"{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;NewFeatures&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:true}\" await-children><section id=\"features\" class=\"relative px-6 py-24 md:py-32\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white opacity-0\" style=\"animation:featureFadeUp 0.7s ease-out 0.1s forwards\">Engineered for<!-- --> <span class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-500 via-emerald-400 to-teal-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent\">Performance</span></h2><p class=\"mt-5 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-400 opacity-0\" style=\"animation:featureFadeUp 0.7s ease-out 0.25s forwards\">Our infrastructure is built for high-throughput AI workloads without the overhead of token-based pricing.</p></div><div class=\"mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 gap-5 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"group rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.06] bg-white/[0.02] p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-brand-500/30 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-brand-500/[0.04] opacity-0\" style=\"animation:featureFadeUp 0.6s ease-out 0.35s forwards\"><div class=\"mb-4 inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-500/10 text-brand-500 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:bg-brand-500/15\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap h-5 w-5\"><polygon points=\"13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2\"></polygon></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white\">Zero Token Limits</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-400\">Code as much as you want. We charge for concurrency, not tokens. Ideal for heavy AI workflows.</p></div><div class=\"group rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.06] bg-white/[0.02] p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-brand-500/30 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-brand-500/[0.04] opacity-0\" style=\"animation:featureFadeUp 0.6s ease-out 0.44999999999999996s forwards\"><div class=\"mb-4 inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-500/10 text-brand-500 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:bg-brand-500/15\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-server h-5 w-5\"><rect width=\"20\" height=\"8\" x=\"2\" y=\"2\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><rect width=\"20\" height=\"8\" x=\"2\" y=\"14\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><line x1=\"6\" x2=\"6.01\" y1=\"6\" y2=\"6\"></line><line x1=\"6\" x2=\"6.01\" y1=\"18\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white\">High-Performance API</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-400\">Engineered for maximum throughput and minimal latency to support complex agentic coding workflows.</p></div><div class=\"group rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.06] bg-white/[0.02] p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-brand-500/30 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-brand-500/[0.04] opacity-0\" style=\"animation:featureFadeUp 0.6s ease-out 0.55s forwards\"><div class=\"mb-4 inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-500/10 text-brand-500 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:bg-brand-500/15\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-cpu h-5 w-5\"><rect x=\"4\" y=\"4\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" rx=\"2\"></rect><rect x=\"9\" y=\"9\" width=\"6\" height=\"6\"></rect><path d=\"M15 2v2\"></path><path d=\"M15 20v2\"></path><path d=\"M2 15h2\"></path><path d=\"M2 9h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 15h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 9h2\"></path><path d=\"M9 2v2\"></path><path d=\"M9 20v2\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white\">State-of-the-Art Models</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-400\">Access top-tier open source foundation models natively integrated and optimized for codebase reasoning.</p></div><div class=\"group rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.06] bg-white/[0.02] p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-brand-500/30 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-brand-500/[0.04] opacity-0\" style=\"animation:featureFadeUp 0.6s ease-out 0.65s forwards\"><div class=\"mb-4 inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-500/10 text-brand-500 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:bg-brand-500/15\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-activity h-5 w-5\"><path d=\"M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white\">Always On</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-400\">No cold starts. Your dedicated lanes are reserved and ready when you are.</p></div><div class=\"group rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.06] bg-white/[0.02] p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-brand-500/30 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-brand-500/[0.04] opacity-0\" style=\"animation:featureFadeUp 0.6s ease-out 0.75s forwards\"><div class=\"mb-4 inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-500/10 text-brand-500 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:bg-brand-500/15\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users h-5 w-5\"><path d=\"M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white\">Team Collaboration</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-400\">Shared workspaces, usage analytics, and centralized billing for teams of any size.</p></div><div class=\"group rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.06] bg-white/[0.02] p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-brand-500/30 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-brand-500/[0.04] opacity-0\" style=\"animation:featureFadeUp 0.6s ease-out 0.85s forwards\"><div class=\"mb-4 inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-500/10 text-brand-500 transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:bg-brand-500/15\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield h-5 w-5\"><path d=\"M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white\">Privacy &amp; Compliance</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-400\">Your code never touches training sets or external logs. SOC-2 compliant infrastructure.</p></div></div></div><style>\n      </style></section><!--astro:end--></astro-island> <astro-island uid=\"juvnP\" prefix=\"r11\" component-url=\"/_astro/NewPricing.B8vEW0s3.js\" component-export=\"default\" renderer-url=\"/_astro/client.BUMBIz6o.js\" props=\"{}\" ssr client=\"visible\" opts=\"{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;NewPricing&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:true}\" await-children><section id=\"pricing\" class=\"relative py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl\"><div class=\"mb-16 text-center\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white\">Simple, transparent pricing</h2><p class=\"mt-4 text-base text-gray-400\">Pay for concurrency, not tokens. Scale lanes as your team grows.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 max-w-5xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"relative flex flex-col rounded-2xl border p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover: