{"type":"message","id":"acf3b501","parentId":"f06de53f","timestamp":"2026-04-03T14:42:05.448Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我看到会话配置很复杂。让我检查OpenClaw的文档，看看如何在Control UI中启用模型切换。根据OpenClaw的架构，模型切换通常是通过在`agents.defaults`配置中设置`modelSelector`或类似选项。\n\n让我尝试一个更直接的方法：检查OpenClaw的Dashboard，看看是否有模型切换功能："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_4c9sdpR8CKquW9wrNwKpigJ3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s http://127.0.0.1:18789/api/status 2>&1 | head -50"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":28666,"output":137,"cacheRead":19392,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48195,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775227303024,"responseId":"11145967-6749-4c52-8a93-8a95a4dc6474"}}
