{"type":"message","id":"4809bdab","parentId":"fb1b8cbc","timestamp":"2026-04-03T14:48:01.789Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我看到会话文件中有`model_change`事件。理论上，我可以通过添加新的`model_change`事件来切换模型。但是，这需要了解OpenClaw的内部事件格式。\n\n## 方法5：探索OpenClaw Control UI的实际功能\n\n让我尝试直接访问Dashboard，看看是否有隐藏的模型切换功能。首先，让我检查Dashboard的HTML结构："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_j8iKvnNzx3wIGXeT60S75QBX","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s http://127.0.0.1:18789/ | grep -o 'data-model=\"[^\"]*\"' | head -5"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":429,"output":147,"cacheRead":46720,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47296,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775227672516,"responseId":"b7fc8cb9-758d-4202-afa9-aee48c71c0f9"}}
