{"type":"message","id":"7703d728","parentId":"38d74135","timestamp":"2026-04-03T14:48:24.854Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 基于OpenClaw架构的分析\n\n根据我对OpenClaw的了解，Control UI的模型切换功能可能有几种实现方式：\n\n### 可能性1：通过JavaScript动态切换\nControl UI可能在前端JavaScript中实现了模型切换，但需要特定的配置才能启用。\n\n### 可能性2：通过URL参数\n有些OpenClaw部署支持URL参数，例如：\n- `?model=codingplan/minimax-m2.5`\n- `?provider=codingplan`\n\n### 可能性3：通过会话创建参数\n创建新会话时可以指定模型参数。\n\n## 建议的解决方案\n\n基于当前情况，我建议：\n\n### 方案A：创建新的专用会话\n创建一个专门使用CodingPlan模型的新会话，你可以在浏览器中打开两个标签页：\n- 标签1：当前会话（使用DeepSeek）\n- 标签2：新会话（使用CodingPlan）\n\n### 方案B：探索Control UI的隐藏功能\n让我尝试一些常见的URL参数模式："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_zhLPKqHvcfxWyTMMKPS3leRb","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"测试URL参数...\" && for param in \"model=codingplan/minimax-m2.5\" \"provider=codingplan\" \"model=minimax-m2.5\" \"modelOverride=codingplan/minimax-m2.5\"; do echo \"测试: ?$param\"; curl -s \"http://127.0.0.1:18789/?$param\" | grep -i \"model\\|error\\|not\" | head -2; echo \"---\"; done"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":42,"output":348,"cacheRead":47360,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47750,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775227689446,"responseId":"a40f03a9-1ba6-4aa1-a82b-6035d30f9c0d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"76aa34ca","parentId":"7703d728","timestamp":"2026-04-03T14:48:24.929Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_zhLPKqHvcfxWyTMMKPS3leRb","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"测试URL参数...\n测试: ?model=codingplan/minimax-m2.5\n        var THEMES = { claw: 1, knot: 1, dash: 1 };\n          openknot: \"knot:dark\",\n---\n测试: ?provider=codingplan\n        var THEMES = { claw: 1, knot: 1, dash: 1 };\n          openknot: \"knot:dark\",\n---\n测试: ?model=minimax-m2.5\n        var THEMES = { claw: 1, knot: 1, dash: 1 };\n          openknot: \"knot:dark\",\n---\n测试: ?modelOverride=codingplan/minimax-m2.5\n        var THEMES = { claw: 1, knot: 1, dash: 1 };\n          openknot: \"knot:dark\",\n---"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":55,"aggregated":"测试URL参数...\n测试: ?model=codingplan/minimax-m2.5\n        var THEMES = { claw: 1, knot: 1, dash: 1 };\n          openknot: \"knot:dark\",\n---\n测试: ?provider=codingplan\n        var THEMES = { claw: 1, knot: 1, dash: 1 };\n          openknot: \"knot:dark\",\n---\n测试: ?model=minimax-m2.5\n        var THEMES = { claw: 1, knot: 1, dash: 1 };\n          openknot: \"knot:dark\",\n---\n测试: ?modelOverride=codingplan/minimax-m2.5\n        var THEMES = { claw: 1, knot: 1, dash: 1 };\n          openknot: \"knot:dark\",\n---","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775227704926}}
{"type":"message","id":"893259a4","parentId":"76aa34ca","timestamp":"2026-04-03T14:48:35.151Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"URL参数似乎没有影响页面内容。让我尝试**方案C：检查OpenClaw的配置文档**。\n\n根据OpenClaw的文档，模型切换功能可能需要配置`agents.defaults`。让我检查是否有相关的配置示例："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_H61DKetUMrsPH8g0chGaCXfR","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find ~/.nvm/versions/node/v22.22.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw -name \"*.md\" -type f | xargs grep -l \"modelSelector\\|model switch\" 2>/dev/null | head -5"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":215,"output":139,"cacheRead":47744,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48098,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775227704929,"responseId":"162f155f-ab19-45ca-8018-d0afa6855d38"}}
