{"type":"message","id":"ee8581f7","parentId":"06201403","timestamp":"2026-04-03T15:24:09.669Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"很好！CodingPlan API工作正常。现在的问题是OpenClaw没有正确加载CodingPlan模型配置。\n\n## 当前状态总结：\n\n### ✅ **已完成的配置：**\n1. **CodingPlan API配置** - 在`openclaw.json`中已正确配置\n2. **agents.defaults配置** - 已添加，设置CodingPlan为默认模型\n3. **网关服务** - 正在运行\n\n### ❌ **存在的问题：**\n1. **模型列表不显示CodingPlan** - `openclaw models list`没有显示CodingPlan模型\n2. **配置可能未生效** - 需要验证配置是否被正确加载\n\n### 🔧 **可能的解决方案：**\n\n#### 方案1：完全重启网关服务\n```bash\nsystemctl --user stop openclaw-gateway.service\nsystemctl --user start openclaw-gateway.service\n```\n\n#### 方案2：检查配置语法\n验证`openclaw.json`的JSON语法是否正确。\n\n#### 方案3：使用热重载\n有些OpenClaw版本支持热重载配置。\n\n**你想让我尝试哪种方案？**\n\n另外，我可以先检查一下配置文件的JSON语法："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_DEbR2gH4rDphp4FuEUZhSWJD","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -m json.tool ~/.config/openclaw/openclaw.json > /dev/null && echo \"✅ JSON语法正确\" || echo \"❌ JSON语法错误\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":40,"output":330,"cacheRead":39232,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39602,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775229817193,"responseId":"3f933579-86fb-42c9-85e6-3d235dedb291"}}
